[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    63[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m  [38;2;191;97;106m6[38;2;191;97;106m.[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mThe patient-mediated cross-network query path operates through a separate Cognito-authenticated flow.[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m The Step 4A pseudocode authenticates the originator through the patient-portal Cognito for patient-mediated queries; the Variations / Patient-mediated access through the Patient Access API paragraph names the pattern but does not architect the per-patient authorization-to-source-record-id binding, the abuse-prevention rate-limiting (one patient cannot drive cross-network query cycles for unrelated patients), the audit-attribution discipline distinguishing patient-mediated from staff-initiated queries, or the rejection semantics when the patient's authentication does not bind to a known identity at one of the participants. The audit-trail discipline is recipe-specific because the patient-mediated flow's authentication chain is propagated explicitly through the audit log with the patient's authentication-event-id retained at the participant-level Cognito.[K
